        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">From Survey to Design in Days</h2>
        <a href="/3d-scan-to-bim" class="inline-block bg-white text-blue-600 px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-bold">View Scan to BIM Services</a>
